item.title: Elm Binary Tree Exercises part 1
item.description: Elm Binary Tree exercises As I was working my way through the Elm Guide, I saw that the exercises at the end of this Binary Tree example were reccomended as a way to get a good handle on Union Types. I marked it down for future consideration, and I've finally come back to it. (Note: all of my snippets are coming from the solutions on my github) So far I have implemented the parts that seemed the most straight forward to me.
